@echo off

Rem @Echo off is used to hide the source code.
rem if you wanted to delete @echo off you could.
rem but whoever sees your batch file would see all
rem of the code being executed. @echo off keeps it
rem more cleaner looking. Rem is used to place
rem comments in your code. This means you can add
rem your own text to the code without showing errors
rem on the screen for it.

echo hello world!

rem this displays the line hello world on the screen. 
rem run this batch file and you will see the words
rem hello world on the screen.

pause

rem pause will make the batch file pause until a key
rem is pressed by a user. Since we have not put any 
rem other commands after pause it will exit the batch
rem file.
